data.description: Nestled in a WONDERFUL NEIGHBORHOOD, this charming residence sits on a HUGE CORNER LOT spanning 1.48 ACRES adorned with TREES GALORE! The versatile layout of the living area allows for the creation of 2 separate areas, perfect for personalized use or entertaining guests. Step inside to discover a warm and inviting atmosphere with a touch of elegance, featuring a FORMAL DINING area and a cozy FIREPLACE, creating a focal point in the heart of the home. The SPLIT BEDROOM PLAN ensures privacy, offering a retreat for both homeowners and guests alike. Escape to the the outdoors and unwind on the COVERED BACK PATIO, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or hosting gatherings with loved ones. The SIDE ENTRY GARAGE adds to the curb appeal while providing ample parking space. A large storage building is also available. This property is a true gem, offering a harmonious blend of comfort, style, and functionality in a picturesque setting. Seller is offering a floor allowance.
